    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but my doctor is super busy and i cant get an appointment until next week... i really dont want to miss doses of my cholesterol meds because my levels are already high. if i just take them at different times of the day, like simvastatin in the morning and the antibiotic at night, would that be safe enough? i just need to get through this 7 day course.",
